text.tspan: sshping - Echo Time and Speed Test over ssh connections
A small utility you can use to answer these questions:
-- What is my interactive response time when ssh'd into a remote system?
-- What is my scp file copy thruput speed?
Login to the target system via ssh, getting an interactive shell.
Send one character at a time, measuring latency for each to be echo'd back.
Open an scp subsytem connection to the target
